<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6421] Newify fails for local variable assignment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6421</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    @Newify foo() {
        def x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;(42)
    }
    foo() 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fails with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Caught: groovy.lang.MissingMethodException: No signature of method: newifyBug.Integer() is applicable for argument types: (java.lang.Integer) values: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;44&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
groovy.lang.MissingMethodException: No signature of method: newifyBug.Integer() is applicable for argument types: (java.lang.Integer) values: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;44&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        at newifyBug.foo(newifyBug.groovy:6)&lt;br/&gt;
        at newifyBug.run(newifyBug.groovy:9)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;source: &lt;a href=&quot;http://groovy.329449.n5.nabble.com/Potential-problem-with-Newify-td5717385.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://groovy.329449.n5.nabble.com/Potential-problem-with-Newify-td5717385.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
